  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": "## 5. Train on the GPU\n\nThis uses the LoveDA config with the two T4 speed knobs turned on, namely mixed precision and image size 384. With them a T4 epoch takes about 8 minutes, so 15 epochs finish in roughly 2 to 2.5 hours and reach about 0.50 mean IoU on the validation split. Training at the default 512 with mixed precision off is much slower, around 22 minutes per epoch. Raise train.epochs or drop the image size override for a stronger full resolution run when you have the GPU time."
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": "!python scripts/train.py --config configs/default.yaml --set train.epochs=15 dataloader.batch_size=8 dataloader.num_workers=2 train.amp=true dataset.image_size=[384,384]"
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 6. Evaluate and analyze on the validation split\n",
